dscaping that blends into the forested site. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-entryway-110725-751-01.jpg\" alt=\"The home is accessible from both a driveway and a footpath, reflecting the dual modes of arrival common to the island. The entry sequence is subtle, with minimal hardscape and native landscaping that blends into the forested site. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-entryway-110725-751-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-entryway-110725-751-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-entryway-110725-751-01-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-entryway-110725-751-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-house-entryway-110725-751-01-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/entry-foyer-110725-746-01.jpg\" alt=\"The home is accessible from both a driveway and a footpath, reflecting the dual modes of arrival common to the island. The entry sequence is subtle, with minimal hardscape and native landscaping that blends into the forested site. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/entry-foyer-110725-746-01.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/entry-foyer-110725-746-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/entry-foyer-110725-746-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/entry-foyer-110725-746-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.co