sual focal point. Large Sierra Pacific windows and sliding glass doors open the space to the outdoors, providing cross-ventilation and direct access to surrounding decks.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-01.jpg\" alt=\"Large windows and a corten steel fireplace anchor this open, light-filled living space with views to the water.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-02.jpg\" alt=\"Large windows and a corten steel fireplace anchor this open, light-filled living space with views to the water.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-02-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-02-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-03.jpg\" alt=\"Large windows and a corten steel fireplace anchor this open, light-filled living space with views to the water.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-03-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-03-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/living-room-fireplace-110725-735-03-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLocated between the kitchen and living room, the dining area shares the home’s open floor plan. It’s oriented toward the bluff, with sightlines to the trees and water, and balances earthy warmth with clean, modern lines. Exposed wood grain, black accents, and concrete floors create a grounded palette that feels both relaxed and refined, while sculptural pendant lights cast a soft glow over the long table, setting a quiet, intimate tone.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dining-room-110725-735-01.jpg\" alt=\"A warm, modern dining space with concrete floors, sculptural lighting, and floor-to-ceiling forest views, perfect for slow meals and quiet moments.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dining-room-110725-735-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dining-room-110725-735-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dining-room-110725-735-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dining-room-110725-735-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dining-room-110725-735-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe kitchen is designed for functionality and flow. Ample counter space in the form of two kitchen islands, supports daily use and entertaining, and its adjacency to the main living spaces makes it a natural gathering point. Skylights above the islands bring in daylight and highlight the green stone countertops.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-01.jpg\" alt=\"An open plan kitchen with two islands and skylights, is built for gathering, with clean lines, ample light, and strong indoor-outdoor flow.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-02.jpg\" alt=\"An open plan kitchen with two islands and skylights, is built for gathering, with clean lines, ample light, and strong indoor-outdoor flow.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-02-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-02-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-03.jpg\" alt=\"An open plan kitchen with two islands and skylights, is built for gathering, with clean lines, ample light, and strong indoor-outdoor flow.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-03-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-03-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-03-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-04.jpg\" alt=\"An open plan kitchen with two islands and skylights, is built for gathering, with clean lines, ample light, and strong indoor-outdoor flow.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-04.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-04-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-04-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-04-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/two-island-kitchen-with-skylight-110725-735-04-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-two-island-kitchen-110725-740-01.jpg\" alt=\"An open plan kitchen with two islands and skylights, is built for gathering, with clean lines, ample light, and strong indoor-outdoor flow.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-two-island-kitchen-110725-740-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-two-island-kitchen-110725-740-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-two-island-kitchen-110725-740-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-two-island-kitchen-110725-740-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-two-island-kitchen-110725-740-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-design-110725-744-01.jpg\" alt=\"An open plan kitchen with two islands and skylights, is built for gathering, with clean lines, ample light, and strong indoor-outdoor flow.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-design-110725-744-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-design-110725-744-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-design-110725-744-01-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-design-110725-744-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-design-110725-744-01-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFloating wood treads and crisp white walls define this simple yet striking stairwell. Black handrails and a polished concrete floor add contrast, while a large window brings in natural light and offers a glimpse of the space from outside. A colorful abstract painting breaks up the clean lines, adding a lived-in touch to the otherwise minimal design.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-110725-739-01.jpg\" alt=\"A minimal stairwell with floating wood treads, black accents, and polished concrete—brightened by natural light and playful abstract art.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-110725-739-01.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-110725-739-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-110725-739-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-110725-739-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-110725-739-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-110725-739-01-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eBathed in morning light, the bedroom feels crisp, bright, and effortlessly cozy. Pale walls and soft bedding reflect the sun, while warm wood accents and a textured area rug bring a sense of calm. The sliding glass doors open to forest views and fresh air, inviting the outdoors in. A colorful painting and vintage-style leather chair add personality, making the space feel lived-in and loved, perfect for slow starts and quiet afternoons. A window above the bed allows natural light to filter through to the bathroom.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-110725-732-01.jpg\" alt=\"Crisp white walls, a textured rug, and a vintage leather chair create a relaxed, lived-in feel in this light-filled bedroom retreat.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-110725-732-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-110725-732-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-110725-732-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-110725-732-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-110725-732-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bathroom combines modern simplicity with natural warmth. A floating wood vanity sits beneath a window to the bedroom and a mirror. Nearby, a black-and-white soaking tub rests beside the glass, offering an unobstructed view of the trees. Soft lighting, layered textures, and organic details, like the sculptural branch installation, create a calm, grounded space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-01.jpg\" alt=\"This modern bathroom blends clean lines with natural textures, featuring a floating wood vanity, soaking tub, and views into the surrounding trees.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1708\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-02.jpg\" alt=\"This modern bathroom blends clean lines with natural textures, featuring a floating wood vanity, soaking tub, and views into the surrounding trees.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-02.jpg 1708w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-02-940x1409.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-02-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-02-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-02-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-02-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1708px) 100vw, 1708px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-03.jpg\" alt=\"This modern bathroom blends clean lines with natural textures, featuring a floating wood vanity, soaking tub, and views into the surrounding trees.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-03.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-03-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-03-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-03-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-03-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-freestanding-bathtub-110725-732-03-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis Orcas Island home shows how a well-designed structure can make efficient use of a challenging site while aligning with environmental conditions and lifestyle goals. By prioritizing function, material du